{"tid":1067600,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老母既黑暗料理","createTime":"2019-03-18T15:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T15:49:20.000Z","uid":214670,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53809844e3ba0a059b0a5b30287eb24ed5e219d7","tid":1067600,"uid":214670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"我老母將臭左既豬扒整成蜜汁豬扒，我食左一舊覺得有啲奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我講啲肉係咪臭左？<br />\n我老母竟然同我講，唔洗驚我有用醋「那」過～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之後小佢用醋撚有用臭左就臭左啦！用左醋啲毒素都係到架。然後老母嬲左我.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS.唔係第一次中伏，上次唔知道臭左，一食臭到嘔返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a90d379b2f1f814eb68a8e2a6a68353655f70c","tid":1067600,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:29:01.000Z","msg":"老母用大樹菠羅炒牛肉.食一啖即時倒哂"},{"pid":"74423410ad1936ffda217ade482a1eeb1d6893b6","tid":1067600,"uid":195258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"檸檬魚蛋炒甘藍  本身甘藍就苦苦地 變左又酸又苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豆豉蟹子丸炆雞  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef9bf754355fb89a3c28be9298986070a5c812e","tid":1067600,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"忌廉梳打雞"}]}